<paragraph blockId="6.[151,1437,729,792]" pageId="6" pageNumber="157">
Comments: The 
<typeStatus box="[336,384,730,756]" pageId="6" pageNumber="157">type</typeStatus>
locality cannot be further narrowed down than to 
